Different part of this package come under different licenses.

Memoria itself is under Apache 2.0 license.

Fibers and Filesystem are originally Boost Fibers/Filesystem 1.63.0 and come under 
Boost lincense with copyright hedears of their autors.

Disruptor queue is under BSD-style license embedded in corresponding sources.

Fmt library is under BSD-style license embedded in corresponding sources. See also LICENCE.fmt

Jemalloc is distributed under BSD-style licence. See COPYING.jemalloc for details.

Check file headers to get the exact conditions those sources may be used under.
